        "Requires ATK bridge (at-spi2-atk) to be loaded by applications",
        "No pixel-level control — depends on accessibility tree accuracy",
        "Dependent on application accessibility compliance (GTK3/4, Qt5/6)",
        "No browser DOM access (use Playwright MCP for browser semantic interactions)",
        "Performance varies with accessibility tree depth",
        "Cannot interact with applications that do not expose AT-SPI interfaces"
      ],
      "environment_requirements": [
        "D-Bus session bus running",
        "at-spi2-core daemon running (at-spi-bus-launcher or /usr/libexec/at-spi2-registryd)",
